data.description: Beautifully built custom home with lake views and a great family neighborhood. This home has everything to offer including a large open kitchen w/island, SS appliances, granite countertops, and a huge pantry. Down are 3 bedrooms, jack&jill bath, large living area, & office. Up is 2nd living area, full bath, dinette, wet bar,& bedroom. Can be college/inlaw quarters. Tons of closet & storage space in this home, fenced backyard backs up to green space. Even garage has AC! Lot next door also avail. Sq ft approx
